Parse CHARMM parameter file to get LJ parameters. Replace VMD VdW radii with Rmin/2.  

USAGE

::parseCHARMMpar::VdWassign <molID> <CHARMM parameter file>

molID is the the VMD internal index for the "molecule" (e.g. "top", 0, 1, 2...) 
Check VMD manual. 